<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello <%= name %></h1>
        <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title %>".</p>
        <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">View Reply</a>
        <p class="footer">Thank you for being a part of our community.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
